<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="da">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,100..1000;1,9..40,100..1000&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<title>Vedio Sales</title>
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --p1:#8258a8;--p2:#9470b8;--p3:#a78bca;--p4:#c4a8d8;--p5:#d1b6df;--p6:#e8d9f0;--p7:#f8f3fc;
  --pdark:#5a3a7a;--pdarker:#3d2060;
  --white:#ffffff;--gray:#6b7280;--gray2:#9ca3af;--gray3:#e5e7eb;--gray4:#f3f4f6;
  --green:#16a34a;--greenbg:#dcfce7;--red:#dc2626;--redbg:#fee2e2;
  --blue:#2563eb;--bluebg:#dbeafe;--amber:#d97706;--amberbg:#fef3c7;
  --border:rgba(130,88,168,0.15);--border2:rgba(130,88,168,0.3);
}
body{font-family:"DM Sans",system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:var(--pdarker);background:var(--p7);height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px;height:4px}::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--p6)}::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--p4);border-radius:3px}

/* APP SHELL */
.app{display:flex;flex:1;overflow:hidden;height:calc(100vh - 0px)}
.sidebar{width:280px;min-width:280px;flex-shrink:0;background:var(--p1);display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden}
.main{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden;background:var(--p7)}

/* SIDEBAR */
.sb-logo{padding:20px;border-bottom:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;flex-shrink:0}
.sb-logo img{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:0;object-fit:contain}
.sb-logo-text{color:#fff;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.3px;line-height:1.2}
.sb-logo-sub{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase}

.sb-nav{padding:8px 12px;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px}
.sb-nav a{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:10px 12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-size:14px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;border-radius:8px;transition:all .12s;user-select:none}
.sb-nav a:hover{color:#fff;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)}
.sb-nav a.on{color:#fff;background:rgba(255,255,255,.2)}
.sb-nav .ico{width:18px;height:18px;flex-shrink:0;opacity:.85;stroke-width:1.8}
.sb-nav a.on .ico{opacity:1}

/* FILTER ACCORDION */
.sb-filters{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;overflow-x:hidden}
.acc-hd{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:7px 14px;cursor:pointer;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
.acc-hd:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.05)}
.acc-title{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.8px}
.acc-arrow{font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);transition:transform .15s}
.acc-arrow.open{transform:rotate(180deg)}
.acc-body{padding:8px 12px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);display:none}
.acc-body.open{display:block}
.fl{font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);margin-bottom:3px;margin-top:7px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.3px}
.fl:first-child{margin-top:0}
.fi,.fs{width:100%;padding:5px 8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);border-radius:5px;color:#fff;font-size:11.5px;font-family:inherit;outline:none;transition:border .1s}
.fi:focus,.fs:focus{border-color:var(--p5);background:rgba(255,255,255,.15)}
.fi::placeholder{color:rgba(255,255,255,.35)}
.frow{display:flex;gap:4px;align-items:center}
.frow .fi{flex:1}
.frow span{color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);font-size:11px;flex-shrink:0}
.tog-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:4px 0}
.tog-row label{font-size:11.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);cursor:pointer}
.tog{position:relative;width:30px;height:17px;flex-shrink:0}
.tog input{opacity:0;width:0;height:0;position:absolute}
.tog-sl{position:absolute;inset:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;transition:background .2s}
.tog-sl:before{content:'';position:absolute;width:13px;height:13px;left:2px;top:2px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.5);border-radius:50%;transition:all .2s}
.tog input:checked+.tog-sl{background:var(--p5)}
.tog input:checked+.tog-sl:before{transform:translateX(13px);background:#fff}
.rk-grp{display:flex;gap:3px;margin-top:4px}
.rk-btn{flex:1;padding:4px 2px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);border-radius:5px;font-size:10px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);background:transparent;font-family:inherit;transition:all .12s}
.rk-btn.on{background:rgba(255,255,255,.85);color:var(--p1);border-color:transparent;font-weight:700}
.chip-grp{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:3px;margin-top:4px}
.chip{padding:3px 7px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);border-radius:10px;font-size:10.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);cursor:pointer;user-select:none;transition:all .12s}
.chip:hover{color:rgba(255,255,255,.8)}
.chip.on{background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);border-color:var(--p5);color:#fff}

/* SIDEBAR LISTS */
.sb-lists-wrap{flex-shrink:0;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12)}
.sb-sec{padding:8px 14px 3px;font-size:9px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;font-weight:700}
.sb-li{display:flex;align-items:center;padding:5px 8px 5px 14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);font-size:11.5px;cursor:pointer;gap:4px;transition:color .1s}
.sb-li:hover{color:rgba(255,255,255,.8)}
.sb-li.on{color:#fff}
.sb-li-nm{flex:1;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap}
.sb-li-c{font-size:10px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:8px;flex-shrink:0}
.sb-li.on .sb-li-c{background:rgba(255,255,255,.25)}
.sb-li-del{font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);transition:color .1s;flex-shrink:0}
.sb-li-del:hover{color:rgba(255,255,255,.8)}
.sb-addlist{padding:5px 14px 8px;color:rgba(209,182,223,.7);font-size:11.5px;cursor:pointer;transition:color .1s}
.sb-addlist:hover{color:var(--p5)}
.nlinput{width:calc(100% - 20px);margin:3px 10px;padding:4px 8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);border-radius:5px;color:#fff;font-size:11px;outline:none;font-family:inherit}
.nlinput:focus{border-color:var(--p5)}
.sb-footer{padding:10px}
.exp-btn{width:100%;padding:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);color:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25);border-radius:8px;font-size:11.5px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;transition:all .12s}
.exp-btn:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.25)}

/* FILTER POPOVER */
.filter-btn{position:relative}
.filter-btn .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.filter-btn .filter-count{background:var(--p1);color:#fff;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:8px;min-width:16px;text-align:center}
.filter-popover{display:none;position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 6px);right:0;width:380px;max-height:80vh;overflow-y:auto;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(130,88,168,.18);z-index:100;padding:0}
.filter-popover.open{display:block}
.filter-popover .fp-hd{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:14px 16px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;top:0;background:#fff;border-radius:12px 12px 0 0;z-index:1}
.filter-popover .fp-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker)}
.filter-popover .fp-close{width:28px;height:28px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border:none;background:var(--p7);border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--gray);font-size:16px;transition:all .1s}
.filter-popover .fp-close:hover{background:var(--p6);color:var(--pdarker)}
.filter-popover .fp-section{padding:12px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.filter-popover .fp-section:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.filter-popover .fp-section-title{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.8px;margin-bottom:10px}
.filter-popover .fl{font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);margin-bottom:4px;margin-top:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.3px}
.filter-popover .fl:first-child{margin-top:0}
.filter-popover .fi,.filter-popover .fs{width:100%;padding:7px 10px;background:var(--p7);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;color:var(--pdarker);font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;outline:none;transition:border .1s}
.filter-popover .fi:focus,.filter-popover .fs:focus{border-color:var(--p1);background:#fff;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(130,88,168,.08)}
.filter-popover .fi::placeholder{color:var(--gray2)}
.filter-popover .frow{display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center}
.filter-popover .frow .fi{flex:1}
.filter-popover .frow span{color:var(--gray2);font-size:12px;flex-shrink:0}
.filter-popover .rk-grp{display:flex;gap:4px;margin-top:6px}
.filter-popover .rk-btn{flex:1;padding:6px 4px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;font-size:11px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;color:var(--gray);background:#fff;font-family:inherit;transition:all .12s}
.filter-popover .rk-btn.on{background:var(--p1);color:#fff;border-color:var(--p1);font-weight:700}
.filter-popover .chip-grp{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;margin-top:6px}
.filter-popover .chip{padding:5px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--gray);cursor:pointer;user-select:none;transition:all .12s;background:#fff}
.filter-popover .chip:hover{color:var(--pdarker);border-color:var(--p3)}
.filter-popover .chip.on{background:var(--p6);border-color:var(--p1);color:var(--pdarker);font-weight:600}
.filter-popover .fp-footer{padding:12px 16px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;bottom:0;background:#fff;border-radius:0 0 12px 12px}
.fp-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:99}
.fp-overlay.open{display:block}

/* TOOLBAR */
.toolbar{padding:9px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;flex-shrink:0;background:var(--white)}
.sb-toggle{width:28px;height:28px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:7px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--p1);background:var(--p7);font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0;transition:all .1s}
.sb-toggle:hover{background:var(--p6)}
.sbox{position:relative;flex:1;min-width:120px}
.sbox input{width:100%;padding:7px 10px 7px 30px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:8px;color:var(--pdarker);font-size:12.5px;outline:none;font-family:inherit;background:var(--p7);transition:all .12s}
.sbox input:focus{border-color:var(--p1);background:#fff;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(130,88,168,.1)}
.sbox input::placeholder{color:var(--gray2)}
.sbox-ico{position:absolute;left:9px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);color:var(--p3);font-size:14px;pointer-events:none}
.btn{padding:6px 11px;background:var(--p7);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:7px;color:var(--p1);font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;white-space:nowrap;transition:all .12s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-weight:500}
.btn:hover{background:var(--p6);border-color:var(--p1)}
.btn-primary{background:var(--p1);color:#fff;border-color:var(--p1)}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--pdark);border-color:var(--pdark)}
.btn-sm{padding:4px 9px;font-size:11px}
.btn-danger{color:var(--red);border-color:rgba(220,38,38,.25)}
.btn-danger:hover{background:var(--redbg)}
.btn-amber{color:var(--amber);border-color:rgba(217,119,6,.25)}
.btn-amber:hover{background:var(--amberbg)}
.btn-green{color:var(--green);border-color:rgba(22,163,74,.25)}
.btn-green:hover{background:var(--greenbg)}

/* LEADS LIST BAR */
.leads-list-bar{padding:8px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;background:var(--white);flex-shrink:0}
.llb-lists{display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;flex:1}
.llb-list{padding:5px 12px;border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;color:var(--gray);background:transparent;border:1px solid transparent;transition:all .12s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;user-select:none}
.llb-list:hover{background:var(--p7);color:var(--pdarker)}
.llb-list.on{background:var(--p6);color:var(--p1);font-weight:600;border-color:var(--border)}
.llb-list .llb-count{font-size:10px;background:var(--p7);padding:1px 6px;border-radius:8px;color:var(--gray2)}
.llb-list.on .llb-count{background:var(--p1);color:#fff}
.llb-list .llb-del{font-size:11px;color:var(--gray2);cursor:pointer;margin-left:2px;transition:color .1s}
.llb-list .llb-del:hover{color:var(--red)}
.llb-actions{display:flex;gap:5px;align-items:center;flex-shrink:0}
.llb-input{padding:5px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;outline:none;width:140px;color:var(--pdarker);background:var(--p7)}
.llb-input:focus{border-color:var(--p1);background:#fff}

/* STATUS + SEL BARS */
.stbar{padding:5px 12px;background:var(--p7);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-shrink:0;flex-wrap:wrap}
.stbar .hi{color:var(--p1);font-weight:600}
.selbar{padding:6px 12px;background:var(--p6);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border2);font-size:12px;color:var(--pdark);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;flex-shrink:0;flex-wrap:wrap}
.selbar.h{display:none}

/* BODY */
.body-wrap{flex:1;display:flex;overflow:hidden}
.tw{flex:1;overflow:auto}

/* TABLE */
table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;table-layout:fixed}
th{padding:8px 10px;text-align:left;font-size:10px;color:var(--gray);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);position:sticky;top:0;background:var(--white);z-index:5;font-weight:700;user-select:none;white-space:nowrap}
th.sort{cursor:pointer}th.sort:hover{color:var(--p1)}th.sorted{color:var(--p1)}
td{padding:8px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap;vertical-align:middle}
tr:hover td{background:var(--p7);cursor:pointer}
tr.sel td{background:var(--p6)}
tr.chk td{background:var(--bluebg)}
.co-name{font-weight:600;color:var(--pdarker);font-size:12.5px}
.pill{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600}
.pill-active{background:var(--greenbg);color:var(--green)}
.pill-inactive{background:var(--gray4);color:var(--gray)}
.pill-p1{background:var(--p6);color:var(--pdark)}
.score-stars{color:var(--amber);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:-1px}
.stage-pill{font-size:10px;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap}
.s-new{background:#e0f2fe;color:#0369a1}
.s-qual{background:#f0fdf4;color:#15803d}
.s-dialog{background:#fef9c3;color:#854d0e}
.s-prop{background:#fdf2f8;color:#86198f}
.s-won{background:#dcfce7;color:#166534}
.s-lost{background:#fee2e2;color:#991b1b}
.ib{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:22px;height:22px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:5px;cursor:pointer;background:transparent;color:var(--p3);font-size:11px;font-family:inherit;transition:all .12s}
.ib:hover{background:var(--p6);color:var(--p1);border-color:var(--p1)}
.ib.added{color:var(--green);border-color:rgba(22,163,74,.3);background:var(--greenbg)}
.ib.rm:hover{background:var(--redbg);color:var(--red)}
.cb{width:13px;height:13px;accent-color:var(--p1);cursor:pointer}

/* DETAIL PANEL — fixed overlay, works from any view */
.dp{width:340px;overflow-y:auto;background:var(--white)}
.dp.h{display:none!important}
.dp-head{padding:12px 14px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start}
.dp-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker);line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:2px}
.dp-cvr{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--gray);font-family:monospace}
.dp-close{font-size:20px;color:var(--gray2);cursor:pointer;line-height:1;flex-shrink:0;transition:color .1s}
.dp-close:hover{color:var(--pdarker)}
.dp-tabs{display:flex;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0;overflow-x:auto}
.dp-tab{padding:7px 10px;font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);cursor:pointer;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;white-space:nowrap;transition:all .12s;font-weight:500}
.dp-tab:hover{color:var(--p1)}
.dp-tab.on{color:var(--p1);border-bottom-color:var(--p1);font-weight:600}
.dp-body{display:none;padding:10px 14px}
.dp-body.on{display:block}
.dp-stat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5px;margin-bottom:10px}
.dp-stat{background:var(--p7);border-radius:7px;padding:8px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border)}
.dp-stat-l{font-size:9px;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:2px}
.dp-stat-v{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker)}
.dp-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);font-size:11.5px;gap:6px}
.dp-row:last-of-type{border:none}
.dp-k{color:var(--gray);flex-shrink:0;font-weight:500}
.dp-v{color:var(--pdarker);text-align:right;word-break:break-word;max-width:160px}
.dp-v a{color:var(--blue);text-decoration:none}
.dp-v a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
.dp-section{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.6px;margin:10px 0 4px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3)}

/* SOCIAL ICONS */
.social-links{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:4px}
.soc-ico{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;transition:all .12s;border:1px solid var(--border)}
.soc-ico:hover{transform:scale(1.1)}
.soc-ico svg{width:16px;height:16px;flex-shrink:0}
.soc-ig{background:#fce7f3;border-color:#f9a8d4;color:#be185d}
.soc-fb{background:#eff6ff;border-color:#93c5fd;color:#1d4ed8}
.soc-tt{background:#f0fdf4;border-color:#86efac;color:#166534}
.soc-li{background:#eff6ff;border-color:#93c5fd;color:#0369a1}
.soc-web{background:var(--p6);border-color:var(--p4);color:var(--p1)}
.soc-add{background:var(--gray4);border-color:var(--gray3);color:var(--gray);font-size:16px;font-weight:300}

/* ICP SCORE */
.icp-bar{display:flex;gap:3px;align-items:center}
.icp-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;cursor:pointer;transition:all .12s}
.icp-dot.filled{background:var(--amber)}
.icp-dot.empty{background:var(--gray3)}
.icp-dot:hover{transform:scale(1.3)}

/* PIPELINE */
.pipeline-select{width:100%;padding:5px 8px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker);background:var(--p7);outline:none;cursor:pointer}
.pipeline-select:focus{border-color:var(--p1)}

/* NOTES */
.notes-area{width:100%;padding:6px 9px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker);background:var(--p7);outline:none;resize:vertical;min-height:70px;transition:border .1s}
.notes-area:focus{border-color:var(--p1);background:#fff}
.notes-area::placeholder{color:var(--gray2)}

/* FINANS BARS */
.fin-bar-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px}
.fin-bar-lbl{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray);width:80px;flex-shrink:0;text-align:right;font-weight:500}
.fin-bar-track{flex:1;height:7px;background:var(--gray3);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.fin-bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;transition:width .4s}
.fin-bar-val{font-size:11px;color:var(--pdarker);width:60px;flex-shrink:0;text-align:right;font-weight:600}
.fin-tbl{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:11.5px}
.fin-tbl td{padding:4px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);color:var(--gray)}
.fin-tbl td:last-child{text-align:right;color:var(--pdarker);font-weight:600}
.fin-tbl tr:last-child td{border:none}

/* TAGS */
.tag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:10px;font-size:10.5px;background:var(--p6);color:var(--pdark);border:1px solid var(--border);cursor:pointer}
.tag:hover{background:var(--p5)}
.tag-input{border:none;outline:none;font-size:11px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker);background:transparent;width:80px}

/* EMAIL TEMPLATE */
.template-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:7px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:7px;cursor:pointer;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--p1);background:var(--p7);transition:all .12s;width:100%;margin-bottom:4px}
.template-btn:hover{background:var(--p6);border-color:var(--p1)}
.template-btn .lbl{flex:1;text-align:left}
.template-preview{background:var(--p7);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:7px;padding:10px;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--pdarker);line-height:1.5;display:none;margin-top:6px}
.template-preview.open{display:block}

/* ENRICHMENT STATUS */
.enrich-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:4px 0;font-size:11.5px}
.enrich-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
.e-ok{background:var(--green)}
.e-no{background:var(--gray3)}
.e-maybe{background:var(--amber)}

/* MODAL */
.modal-bg{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.5);z-index:100;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.modal-bg.h{display:none}
.modal{background:#fff;border-radius:12px;padding:22px;width:360px;max-height:88vh;overflow-y:auto;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}
.modal h3{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker);margin-bottom:4px}
.modal p{font-size:12px;color:var(--gray);margin-bottom:14px}
.modal-section{margin-bottom:16px;padding-bottom:16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3)}
.modal-section:last-of-type{border:none;margin-bottom:0}
.modal-section h4{font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker);margin-bottom:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.modal input{width:100%;padding:7px 9px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:7px;color:var(--pdarker);font-size:12px;outline:none;font-family:inherit;margin-bottom:5px;background:var(--p7);transition:border .1s}
.modal input:focus{border-color:var(--p1)}
.modal input::placeholder{color:var(--gray2)}
.modal-actions{display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:flex-end;margin-top:14px}
.int-status{font-size:10px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600}
.int-ok{background:var(--greenbg);color:var(--green)}
.int-no{background:var(--gray4);color:var(--gray)}
.social-note{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--gray);background:var(--amberbg);border:1px solid rgba(217,119,6,.2);border-radius:6px;padding:7px 10px;margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.4}

/* TASKS PAGE */
.tasks-page{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:18px 24px}
.tasks-section{margin-bottom:22px}
.tasks-section-hd{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.8px;color:var(--gray2);margin-bottom:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px}
.tasks-cnt{font-size:10px;padding:1px 6px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700}
/* ── Three-day columns ─────────────────────────── */
.tasks-3col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1.25fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:24px}
.tasks-day-col{border-radius:10px;padding:13px 12px;border:1px solid var(--border);min-height:120px;transition:opacity .15s}
.tasks-day-col.day-past{background:var(--p7);opacity:.52}
.tasks-day-col.day-today{background:#fff;border-color:var(--p2);box-shadow:0 2px 14px rgba(130,88,168,.1)}
.tasks-day-col.day-future{background:var(--p7);opacity:.52}
.tasks-day-col:hover{opacity:1}
.tasks-day-hd{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.7px;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.tasks-day-hd .day-label{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.tasks-day-hd .day-cnt{font-size:10px;padding:1px 6px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700}
.tasks-day-col.day-past .tasks-day-hd{color:var(--gray)}
.tasks-day-col.day-today .tasks-day-hd{color:var(--pdarker)}
.tasks-day-col.day-future .tasks-day-hd{color:var(--gray)}
.tasks-day-empty{font-size:11px;color:var(--gray3);text-align:center;padding:18px 0}
.task-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;padding:10px 13px;background:var(--p7);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:6px;transition:all .12s;cursor:default}
.tasks-day-col.day-today .task-item{background:var(--p7)}
.task-item:hover{border-color:var(--p3)}
.task-item.done-task{opacity:.45}
.task-item.overdue{border-color:rgba(220,38,38,.35);background:#fff5f5}
.task-check{width:15px;height:15px;accent-color:var(--p1);cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:3px}
.task-ico{flex-shrink:0;margin-top:0}
.task-body{flex:1;min-width:0}
.task-title{font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--pdarker);margin-bottom:2px;line-height:1.3}
.done-task .task-title{text-decoration:line-through;color:var(--gray2)}
.task-co{font-size:11px;color:var(--p1);font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;display:inline}
.task-co:hover{text-decoration:underline}
.task-meta{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--gray);margin-top:2px}
.task-meta.late{color:var(--red);font-weight:600}
.task-del{font-size:17px;color:var(--gray3);cursor:pointer;transition:color .1s;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;padding:2px}
.task-del:hover{color:var(--red)}
/* Activity add form inside detail panel */
.act-form{background:var(--p7);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:11px;margin-bottom:10px}
.act-form-row{display:flex;gap:5px;margin-bottom:6px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.act-type-sel{padding:5px 7px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;font-size:11px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker);background:var(--white);outline:none;cursor:pointer}
.act-type-sel:focus{border-color:var(--p1)}
.act-inp{flex:1;min-width:100px;padding:5px 8px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;font-size:11.5px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker);background:var(--white);outline:none}
.act-inp:focus{border-color:var(--p1)}
.act-inp::placeholder{color:var(--gray2)}
.act-dt{width:108px}
.act-tm{width:78px}
.act-list-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:7px;padding:7px 9px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);font-size:11.5px}
.act-list-item:last-child{border:none}
.act-list-item.done-act .act-lbl{text-decoration:line-through;color:var(--gray2)}
.act-lbl{flex:1;line-height:1.4}
.act-lbl-meta{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray);display:block;margin-top:1px}
.act-done-cb{width:14px;height:14px;accent-color:var(--p1);cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px}
.act-rm{font-size:14px;color:var(--gray3);cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0}
.act-rm:hover{color:var(--red)}

/* KANBAN DEALS */
.kb-board{display:flex;flex-direction:column;height:100%;overflow:hidden;padding:0 8px 8px}
.kb-cols{display:flex;gap:10px;flex:1;overflow-x:auto;overflow-y:hidden;padding:10px 6px 14px;align-items:stretch}
.kb-col{flex:1;min-width:180px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:var(--white);border-radius:12px;max-height:100%;border:1px solid var(--border)}
.kb-col-hd{padding:14px 14px 12px;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:6px}
.kb-col-name{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.6px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px}
.kb-col-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
.kb-col-meta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.kb-cnt{font-size:10px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;background:var(--p7);color:var(--gray)}
.kb-col-val{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray);font-weight:500}
.kb-cards{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:10px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
.kb-card{background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .12s}
.kb-card:hover{border-color:var(--p3);box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(130,88,168,.1);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.kb-card-name{font-size:13.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker);margin-bottom:3px;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
.kb-card-sub{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--gray);margin-bottom:6px;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
.kb-card-ft{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-top:8px}
.kb-icp{font-size:10px;color:var(--amber)}
.kb-rev{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--pdarker)}
.kb-card-soc{font-size:11px;margin-bottom:5px}
.kb-empty{text-align:center;font-size:11px;color:var(--gray2);padding:24px 8px}
.kb-card-risk-high{border-left:3px solid #f87171!important}
.kb-card-risk-med{border-left:3px solid #fbbf24!important}
.kb-card-flags{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;margin:4px 0}
.kb-card-flag{font-size:11px;color:#dc2626;font-weight:500}
.kb-card-badges{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:6px}
.kb-card-plan{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:5px;border:1px solid var(--border2)}
.kb-card-meta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);margin-top:4px}
.kb-card-meta svg{width:12px;height:12px;stroke:var(--gray2);stroke-width:2;fill:none}
.kb-card a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
.kb-card.dragging{opacity:.35;transform:rotate(1.5deg);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.18)}
.kb-cards.drag-over{background:rgba(130,88,168,.09);outline:2px dashed var(--p3);outline-offset:-4px;border-radius:10px}
.deals-hd{padding:14px 20px;background:transparent;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0}

/* LOGIN OVERLAY */
.login-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:var(--p7);z-index:1000;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.login-card{background:#fff;border-radius:16px;padding:36px 40px;width:340px;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(130,88,168,.18);border:1px solid var(--border)}
.login-logo{text-align:center;margin-bottom:28px}
.login-logo-title{font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:var(--pdarker);margin-bottom:4px;letter-spacing:-.5px}
.login-logo-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--gray2)}
.login-inp{width:100%;padding:10px 12px;border:1.5px solid var(--border2);border-radius:8px;color:var(--pdarker);font-size:13px;outline:none;font-family:inherit;background:var(--p7);transition:border .12s;margin-bottom:10px}
.login-inp:focus{border-color:var(--p1);background:#fff}
.login-inp::placeholder{color:var(--gray2)}
.login-btn{width:100%;padding:11px;background:var(--p1);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;transition:background .12s;margin-top:2px}
.login-btn:hover{background:var(--pdark)}
.login-err{color:var(--red);font-size:11.5px;text-align:center;margin-top:8px;display:none}
.login-hint{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--gray2);text-align:center;margin-top:14px;line-height:1.6}
.login-google-btn{width:100%;padding:11px 16px;background:#fff;color:#3c4043;border:1.5px solid #dadce0;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;transition:box-shadow .15s,border-color .15s;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:16px}
.login-google-btn:hover{box-shadow:0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.12);border-color:#c0c0c0}
.login-google-btn svg{flex-shrink:0}
.login-divider{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:16px}
.login-divider-line{flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border)}
.login-divider-txt{font-size:11px;color:var(--gray2);white-space:nowrap}
.login-fallback{display:none}
.login-fallback.open{display:block}
.login-fallback-toggle{width:100%;background:none;border:none;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--gray2);cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;padding:4px 0;margin-top:4px;text-align:center;transition:color .1s}
.login-fallback-toggle:hover{color:var(--p1)}

/* USER PROFILE (sidebar bottom) */
.user-profile{padding:12px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:auto}
.user-profile-inner{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:12px;border-radius:0;background:transparent !important;cursor:default}
.user-profile-inner:hover{background:transparent !important}
.user-avatar{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;letter-spacing:-.3px}
.user-info{flex:1;min-width:0}
.user-name{font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:#fff;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
.user-role{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);margin-top:2px}
.user-logout{color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);cursor:pointer;transition:color .12s;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;padding:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:relative}
.user-logout:hover{color:rgba(255,255,255,.8)}
.data-tip-popup{position:fixed;background:#1e1e2e;color:#fff;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:6px;white-space:nowrap;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999}
.role-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:5px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px}
.role-sdr{background:rgba(37,99,235,.3);color:#93c5fd}
.role-ae{background:rgba(130,88,168,.3);color:var(--p5)}
.role-admin{background:rgba(217,119,6,.25);color:#fbbf24}

/* DASHBOARD */
.dash-page{padding:22px 28px;max-width:960px}
.dash-hd{margin-bottom:24px}
.dash-greeting{font-size:21px;font-weight:800;color:var(--pdarker);margin-bottom:4px;letter-spacing:-.4px}
.dash-date{font-size:12px;color:var(--gray);text-transform:capitalize}
.dash-section-lbl{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.8px;color:var(--gray2);margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.dash-kpi-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(130px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-bottom:24px}
.dash-kpi{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;position:relative;transition:all .12s}
.dash-kpi:hover{box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(130,88,168,.1)}
.dash-kpi[onclick]:hover{border-color:var(--p3);box-shadow:0 3px 14px rgba(130,88,168,.14);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.dash-kpi-ico{margin-bottom:8px}
.dash-kpi-ico .kpi-icon{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:10px;background:#f1f0f5;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.dash-kpi-ico .kpi-icon svg{width:18px;height:18px;color:#6b7280;stroke-width:1.6}
.dash-kpi-val{font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:var(--pdarker);line-height:1;margin-bottom:4px;letter-spacing:-.5px}
.dash-kpi-lbl{font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);font-weight:500}
.dash-kpi-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray2);margin-top:3px}
.dash-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:24px}
.dash-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:16px}
.dash-card-hd{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.6px;margin-bottom:12px}
.dash-stage-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:9px}
.dash-stage-lbl{width:90px;font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);flex-shrink:0}
.dash-stage-track{flex:1;height:7px;background:var(--gray3);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.dash-stage-fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;transition:width .5s}
.dash-stage-cnt{width:22px;text-align:right;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker);flex-shrink:0}
.dash-act-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3)}
.dash-act-item:last-child{border:none}
.dash-act-ico{flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.dash-act-ico .act-ico{width:32px;height:32px}
.act-ico{display:inline-flex;width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:9px;background:#f1f0f5;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;vertical-align:middle;background-size:16px 16px;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position:center}
.act-call{background-color:#eef2ff;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='%236b7280' stroke-width='2' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z'/%3E%3C/svg%3E")}
.act-email{background-color:#eff6ff;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='%236b7280' stroke-width='2' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Crect x='2' y='4' width='20' height='16' rx='2'/%3E%3Cpath d='m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7'/%3E%3C/svg%3E")}
.act-followup{background-color:#fef3c7;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='%236b7280' stroke-width='2' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M21 2v6h-6M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 15-6.7L21 8M3 22v-6h6M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-15 6.7L3 16'/%3E%3C/svg%3E")}
.act-meeting{background-color:#f3e8ff;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='%236b7280' stroke-width='2' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Crect x='3' y='4' width='18' height='18' rx='2'/%3E%3Cpath d='M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18'/%3E%3C/svg%3E")}
.act-note{background-color:#f0fdf4;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='%236b7280' stroke-width='2' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.5L14.5 2z'/%3E%3Cpath d='M14 2v6h6M16 13H8M16 17H8M10 9H8'/%3E%3C/svg%3E")}
.act-task{background-color:#ecfdf5;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='%236b7280' stroke-width='2' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M9 11l3 3L22 4'/%3E%3Cpath d='M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11'/%3E%3C/svg%3E")}
.dash-act-body{flex:1;min-width:0}
.dash-act-title{font-size:11.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--pdarker);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
.dash-act-meta{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray);margin-top:1px}
.dash-team-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3)}
.dash-team-row:last-child{border:none}
.dash-team-av{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:10px;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0}
.dash-team-name{flex:1;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--pdarker)}
.dash-team-stat{font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);text-align:right}

/* DASHBOARD LIGHT MODULES */
#dashboard-panel{background:var(--p7)!important}
.dm-page{padding:24px 28px;min-height:100%;box-sizing:border-box}
.dm-hd{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:28px}
.dm-greeting{font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:var(--pdarker);letter-spacing:-.5px;margin-bottom:4px}
.dm-date{font-size:12px;color:var(--gray);text-transform:capitalize}
.dm-live{font-size:11px;color:var(--gray2);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.dm-live-dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:#10b981;flex-shrink:0;animation:dmPulse 2s infinite}
@keyframes dmPulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.4}}
.dm-kpi-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(140px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-bottom:12px}
.dm-kpi{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;position:relative;transition:border-color .15s,transform .15s,box-shadow .15s}
.dm-kpi[onclick]{cursor:pointer}
.dm-kpi[onclick]:hover{border-color:var(--p3);transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(130,88,168,.12)}
.dm-kpi-ico{margin-bottom:10px}
.dm-kpi-ico .kpi-icon{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:10px;background:#f1f0f5;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.dm-kpi-ico .kpi-icon svg{width:18px;height:18px;color:#6b7280;stroke-width:1.6}
.dm-kpi-val{font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:var(--pdarker);line-height:1;margin-bottom:4px;letter-spacing:-.6px}
.dm-kpi-lbl{font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);font-weight:500}
.dm-kpi-sub{font-size:10px;margin-top:6px}
.dm-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:2px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:5px}
.dm-badge-up{background:rgba(5,150,105,.09);color:#059669}
.dm-badge-down{background:rgba(220,38,38,.09);color:#dc2626}
.dm-badge-neu{background:rgba(130,88,168,.08);color:var(--p1)}
.dm-kpi-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:12px}
.dm-attention-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:3fr 2fr;gap:12px}
.dm-attn-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);cursor:pointer;transition:background .1s}
.dm-attn-item:hover{background:var(--p7)}
.dm-attn-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.dm-attn-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
.dm-attn-info{flex:1;min-width:0}
.dm-attn-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--pdarker)}
.dm-attn-detail{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray);margin-top:2px}
.dm-attn-badge{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:5px;flex-shrink:0;white-space:nowrap}
.dm-attn-badge.risk{background:#fee2e2;color:#dc2626}
.dm-attn-badge.overdue{background:#fef3c7;color:#d97706}
.dm-attn-badge.stale{background:#e0e7ff;color:#4f46e5}
.dm-timeline-item{display:flex;gap:12px;padding:10px 16px;position:relative}
.dm-timeline-item:not(:last-child){border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3)}
.dm-timeline-date{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray);width:42px;flex-shrink:0;font-weight:600;padding-top:2px}
.dm-timeline-body{flex:1;min-width:0}
.dm-timeline-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--pdarker)}
.dm-timeline-meta{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray);margin-top:2px}
.dm-win-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);cursor:pointer;transition:background .1s}
.dm-win-item:hover{background:var(--p7)}
.dm-win-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.dm-win-check{width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;background:#dcfce7;color:#16a34a;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;flex-shrink:0;font-weight:700}
.dm-win-info{flex:1;min-width:0}
.dm-win-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--pdarker)}
.dm-win-detail{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray);margin-top:2px}
.dm-win-val{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--green);flex-shrink:0}
.dm-win-date{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray);flex-shrink:0;min-width:70px;text-align:right}
.dm-scorecard-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:12px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3)}
.dm-scorecard-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.dm-scorecard-lbl{flex:1;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--pdarker)}
.dm-scorecard-val{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;min-width:60px;text-align:right}
.dm-scorecard-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
@media(max-width:960px){.dm-kpi-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
@media(max-width:860px){.dm-attention-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
@media(max-width:500px){.dm-kpi-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
/* ── Dashboard module drag system ───────────────────────────────────── */
.dm-modules-wrap{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px}
.dm-module{position:relative;border-radius:12px;transition:opacity .18s,box-shadow .18s}
.dm-module.dm-dragging{opacity:.38;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.14)}
.dm-module.dm-drag-over{outline:2px dashed var(--p3);outline-offset:3px}
.dm-handle-bar{display:none;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:6px 10px 6px 8px;background:rgba(130,88,168,.06);border-radius:8px 8px 0 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(130,88,168,.12);cursor:grab;user-select:none;margin-bottom:-2px}
.dm-edit-active .dm-handle-bar{display:flex}
.dm-handle-icon{font-size:15px;color:var(--p3);line-height:1}
.dm-handle-lbl{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray);flex:1}
.dm-hide-btn{border:none;background:none;font-size:13px;color:var(--gray2);cursor:pointer;padding:2px 5px;border-radius:4px;line-height:1;transition:background .12s}
.dm-hide-btn:hover{background:#fee2e2;color:#dc2626}
.dm-edit-active .dm-module{border:1px dashed rgba(130,88,168,.2);border-radius:12px;background:#fff}
.dm-restore-bar{display:none;border:2px dashed var(--border2);border-radius:10px;padding:12px 16px;background:#fafafa;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:14px}
.dm-restore-bar.has-hidden{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.dm-restore-btn{padding:5px 12px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:7px;background:#fff;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;color:var(--gray);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;transition:all .12s}
.dm-restore-btn:hover{border-color:var(--p1);color:var(--p1)}
.dm-customize-btn{padding:5px 13px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:7px;background:#fff;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;color:var(--gray);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;transition:all .12s}
.dm-customize-btn:hover{border-color:var(--p1);color:var(--p1)}
.dm-customize-btn.dm-active{background:var(--p1);color:#fff;border-color:var(--p1)}
.dm-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:18px}
.dm-card-hd{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.9px;margin-bottom:14px}
.dm-act-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;padding:9px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);cursor:pointer;transition:background .1s}
.dm-act-item:hover{background:var(--p7)}
.dm-act-item:last-child{border:none;padding-bottom:12px}
.dm-today-task{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);cursor:pointer;transition:background .12s}
.dm-today-task:hover{background:var(--p7)}
.dm-today-task:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.dm-act-ico{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:9px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.dm-act-ico .act-ico{width:16px;height:16px;background-color:transparent;background-size:contain;border-radius:0}
.dm-act-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--pdarker);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
.dm-act-meta{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray);margin-top:2px}
.dm-legend{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:10px}
.dm-leg-item{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:10px;color:var(--gray)}
.dm-leg-sq{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:2px;flex-shrink:0}
.dm-team-wrap{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:18px;margin-bottom:24px}
.dm-team-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto auto auto;gap:0}
.dm-team-hdr{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.7px;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3)}
.dm-team-hdr.r{text-align:right}
.dm-team-row{display:contents}
.dm-team-cell{padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);font-size:12px;color:var(--gray);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.dm-team-cell.r{justify-content:flex-end;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker)}
.dm-team-cell:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.dm-team-av{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:800;font-size:10px;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0}

/* ── CALLS PANEL ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.cl-page{display:flex;flex-direction:column;height:100%;overflow:hidden}
.cl-hd{padding:12px 20px;background:#fff;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;flex-shrink:0}
.cl-tabs{display:flex;gap:4px;background:var(--p7);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:3px}
.cl-tab{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;padding:5px 16px;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--gray);border:none;background:transparent;transition:all .15s}
.cl-tab.on{background:#fff;color:var(--pdarker);box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
.cl-body{display:flex;flex:1;overflow:hidden;gap:0}
/* Left column: queue */
.cl-queue{width:220px;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;border-right:1px solid var(--border);background:#fff;overflow:hidden}
.cl-queue-hd{padding:12px 14px 8px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.7px;color:var(--gray2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0}
.cl-queue-list{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:8px}
.cl-queue-item{padding:8px 10px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;transition:background .1s;border:1px solid transparent}
.cl-queue-item:hover{background:var(--p7)}
.cl-queue-item.active{background:var(--p7);border-color:var(--p3)}
.cl-queue-item.calling{background:#fdf4ff;border-color:var(--p1)}
.cl-qi-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--pdarker);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;flex:1}
.cl-qi-ph{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray);margin-top:1px}
.cl-qi-badge{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 6px;border-radius:4px;flex-shrink:0}
/* Center: dialer */
.cl-dialer{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden;background:var(--p7)}
.cl-dialer-empty{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--gray2);gap:8px}
.cl-active{display:flex;flex-direction:column;height:100%;overflow:hidden}
.cl-call-hd{background:#fff;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:12px 20px;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px}
.cl-chip{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;background:var(--p7);color:var(--pdarker);padding:3px 8px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);white-space:nowrap}
.cl-timer{font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:var(--pdarker);font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;letter-spacing:-1px}
.cl-call-status{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:12px}
.cl-call-status.live{background:#dcfce7;color:#16a34a}
.cl-call-status.idle{background:var(--p7);color:var(--gray2)}
.cl-call-status.ended{background:#fee2e2;color:#dc2626}
.cl-call-body{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;overflow-x:hidden;display:flex;gap:12px;padding:14px 16px;min-width:0}
/* Script area */
.cl-script-wrap{flex:1;min-width:160px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
.cl-script-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden}
.cl-script-ta{width:100%;flex:1;border:none;outline:none;resize:none;font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;line-height:1.7;color:var(--pdarker);padding:14px 16px;background:transparent;box-sizing:border-box;min-height:160px}
.cl-script-ta:focus{background:rgba(130,88,168,.03)}
.cl-action-btn{width:100%;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:8px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;border:none;cursor:pointer;text-align:left;transition:all .15s;margin-top:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px}
.cl-action-btn:hover{filter:brightness(.93)}
.cl-action-note{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray2);margin-top:2px;line-height:1.4}
/* Notes + outcome side */
.cl-notes-col{width:210px;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
.cl-notes-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:11px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;overflow:visible}
.cl-notes-lbl{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}
.cl-notes-ta{width:100%;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:8px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;resize:none;outline:none;color:var(--pdarker);line-height:1.5;box-sizing:border-box}
.cl-notes-ta:focus{border-color:var(--p3)}
.cl-outcome-sel{width:100%;padding:7px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker);background:#fff;outline:none;cursor:pointer}
.cl-outcome-sel:focus{border-color:var(--p3)}
/* Next-action section */
.cl-nxt-types{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:4px}
.cl-nxt-type{padding:5px 4px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;background:#fff;color:var(--gray);cursor:pointer;text-align:center;transition:all .12s;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
.cl-nxt-type.active{background:var(--p1);color:#fff;border-color:var(--p1)}
.cl-nxt-type:hover:not(.active){background:var(--p7);border-color:var(--p3)}
.cl-nxt-inp{width:100%;padding:7px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker);background:#fff;outline:none;box-sizing:border-box}
.cl-nxt-inp:focus{border-color:var(--p3)}
.cl-nxt-row{display:flex;gap:5px}
.cl-nxt-save{width:100%;padding:8px;border:none;border-radius:7px;background:var(--p1);color:#fff;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;margin-top:2px;transition:opacity .12s}
.cl-nxt-save:hover{opacity:.88}
.cl-nxt-saved{text-align:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#16a34a;padding:4px 0}
/* Ctrl bar */
.cl-ctrl{padding:14px 20px;background:#fff;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-shrink:0}
.cl-btn-call{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:9px 18px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s}
.cl-btn-call.start{background:var(--p1);color:#fff}
.cl-btn-call.start:hover{filter:brightness(1.1)}
.cl-btn-call.end{background:#dc2626;color:#fff}
.cl-btn-call.end:hover{filter:brightness(1.1)}
.cl-btn-save{padding:9px 16px;border-radius:8px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;border:1px solid var(--border);background:#fff;color:var(--pdarker);cursor:pointer}
.cl-btn-save:hover{border-color:var(--p3)}
/* History */
.cl-hist{background:#fff;border-top:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0;max-height:220px;overflow-y:auto}
.cl-hist-hd{padding:10px 20px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.7px;color:var(--gray2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;top:0;background:#fff}
.cl-hist-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:100px 1fr 80px 110px 60px 36px;gap:0;align-items:center;padding:8px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);font-size:11px;color:var(--gray)}
.cl-hist-row:hover{background:var(--p7)}
.cl-hist-row .n{color:var(--pdarker);font-weight:600}
.cl-hist-row .ai-btn{background:rgba(130,88,168,.08);border:none;border-radius:5px;padding:3px 8px;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;color:var(--p1);cursor:pointer}
/* AI feedback */
.cl-ai-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:14px;flex-shrink:0}
.cl-ai-score{font-size:32px;font-weight:900;color:var(--p1);line-height:1}
.cl-ai-list{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
.cl-ai-list li{font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:flex-start}
/* Auto-dial controls */
.cl-autodial{padding:10px 14px;background:var(--p7);border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-shrink:0}
/* ── DEMOS ──── */
.cl-demo-body{display:flex;flex:1;overflow:hidden;gap:0}
.cl-demo-list{width:240px;flex-shrink:0;border-right:1px solid var(--border);background:#fff;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden}
.cl-demo-item{padding:12px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);cursor:pointer;transition:background .1s}
.cl-demo-item:hover{background:var(--p7)}
.cl-demo-item.on{background:#fdf4ff;border-right:3px solid var(--p1)}
.cl-demo-date{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--p1);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:3px}
.cl-demo-co{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker)}
.cl-demo-ct{font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);margin-top:1px}
.cl-demo-status{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;margin-top:4px}
.cl-demo-s-scheduled{background:#dbeafe;color:#1d4ed8}
.cl-demo-s-completed{background:#dcfce7;color:#16a34a}
.cl-demo-s-cancelled{background:#fee2e2;color:#dc2626}
.cl-demo-detail{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:20px;background:var(--p7)}
.cl-demo-section{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:12px}
.cl-demo-sec-hd{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.7px;color:var(--gray2);margin-bottom:10px}
.cl-join-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:10px 20px;background:var(--p1);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;transition:filter .15s}
.cl-join-btn:hover{filter:brightness(1.1)}
.cl-pain-tag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;background:var(--p7);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:5px;padding:3px 8px;font-size:11px;color:var(--pdarker);margin:2px}
.modal-inp{width:100%;padding:8px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:7px;font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker);background:#fff;outline:none;box-sizing:border-box}
.modal-inp:focus{border-color:var(--p3);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(130,88,168,.08)}

/* CONTACTS / DEAL / HISTORY TABS */
.dp-tabs{overflow-x:auto;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--border2) transparent}
.dp-tabs::-webkit-scrollbar{height:3px}
.dp-tabs::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:transparent}
.dp-tabs::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border2);border-radius:2px}
.contact-card{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;background:var(--p7);position:relative;margin-bottom:8px}
.contact-av{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0}
.contact-del{position:absolute;top:7px;right:8px;color:var(--gray3);cursor:pointer;font-size:18px;transition:color .1s;line-height:1}
.contact-del:hover{color:var(--red)}
.contact-form{background:var(--p7);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:9px;padding:12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;margin-bottom:10px}
.contact-inp{padding:6px 9px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker);background:#fff;outline:none;width:100%;transition:border-color .15s}
.contact-inp:focus{border-color:var(--p1)}
.deal-field{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;margin-bottom:10px}
.deal-field label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}
.deal-inp{padding:7px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:7px;font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker);background:var(--p7);outline:none;width:100%;transition:border-color .15s}
.deal-inp:focus{border-color:var(--p1);background:#fff}
.plan-row{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-bottom:14px}
.plan-btn{flex:1;padding:8px 4px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:7px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;color:var(--gray);background:var(--p7);font-family:inherit;transition:all .12s;line-height:1.3}
.plan-btn:hover{border-color:var(--p1);color:var(--p1)}
.plan-btn.sel{background:var(--p1);color:#fff;border-color:var(--p1)}
/* ── Deal Risk ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.risk-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:5px;white-space:nowrap;line-height:1.4;flex-shrink:0}
.risk-high{background:#fee2e2;color:#991b1b}
.risk-med{background:#fef9c3;color:#854d0e}
.risk-flag{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;padding:8px 11px;border-radius:7px;margin-bottom:5px;font-size:11.5px;line-height:1.4}
.risk-flag-high{background:#fff1f2;border:1px solid #fecaca}
.risk-flag-med{background:#fffbeb;border:1px solid #fde68a}
.risk-flag-low{background:#f0fdf4;border:1px solid #bbf7d0}
.risk-flag-icon{font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1}
.risk-flag-body{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px}
.risk-flag-label{font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker)}
.risk-flag-detail{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--gray)}
.risk-ai-box{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--p7) 0%,#f0fdf4 100%);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:12px 14px;font-size:11.5px;line-height:1.5;margin-top:10px}
.risk-level-banner{border-radius:8px;padding:10px 14px;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-weight:600;font-size:12px}
.risk-level-high{background:#fff1f2;border:1px solid #fecaca;color:#991b1b}
.risk-level-med{background:#fffbeb;border:1px solid #fde68a;color:#854d0e}
.risk-level-low{background:#f0fdf4;border:1px solid #bbf7d0;color:#166534}
.risk-level-none{background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--gray)}
.hist-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.hist-item{display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.hist-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.hist-dot{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:3px}
.hist-body{flex:1;min-width:0}
.hist-text{font-size:12px;color:var(--pdarker);line-height:1.4}
.hist-meta{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray2);margin-top:2px}

/* PROFILE MODAL */
.profile-modal-card{background:#fff;border-radius:14px;width:420px;max-width:calc(100vw - 32px);max-height:92vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.28)}
.profile-modal-hd{padding:15px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0}
.profile-modal-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker)}
.profile-modal-close{font-size:22px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--gray2);line-height:1;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;transition:color .1s}
.profile-modal-close:hover{color:var(--pdarker)}
.profile-modal-body{padding:20px;overflow-y:auto;flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px}
.profile-avatar-wrap{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.profile-avatar-ring{position:relative;width:80px;height:80px;cursor:pointer}
.profile-avatar-big{width:80px;height:80px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;overflow:hidden;transition:opacity .15s}
.profile-avatar-ring:hover .profile-avatar-big{opacity:.75}
.profile-avatar-cam{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;opacity:0;transition:opacity .15s;pointer-events:none}
.profile-avatar-ring:hover .profile-avatar-cam{opacity:1}
.profile-avatar-cam-ico{background:rgba(0,0,0,.55);border-radius:50%;padding:7px;font-size:16px;line-height:1}
.profile-field{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px}
.profile-field label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}
.profile-field input{padding:8px 11px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker);background:var(--p7);outline:none;transition:border-color .15s}
.profile-field input:focus{border-color:var(--p1);background:#fff}
.profile-color-row{display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:2px}
.profile-color-swatch{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;cursor:pointer;border:3px solid transparent;transition:transform .12s,border-color .12s}
.profile-color-swatch:hover{transform:scale(1.15)}
.profile-color-swatch.sel{border-color:var(--pdarker)}
.profile-divider{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin:0}
.profile-pw-toggle{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--p1);cursor:pointer;user-select:none;padding:4px 0}
.profile-pw-toggle:hover{color:var(--pdark)}
.profile-pw-section{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
.profile-msg{font-size:11.5px;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:7px;display:none}
.profile-msg.ok{background:var(--greenbg);color:var(--green);display:block}
.profile-msg.err{background:var(--redbg);color:var(--red);display:block}
.profile-modal-ft{padding:12px 20px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:flex-end;flex-shrink:0}

/* EDIT LEAD MODAL */
.edit-lead-card{background:#fff;border-radius:14px;width:480px;max-width:calc(100vw - 32px);max-height:90vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.25)}
.edit-lead-hd{padding:15px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0}
.edit-lead-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker)}
.edit-lead-close{font-size:22px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--gray2);line-height:1;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;transition:color .1s}
.edit-lead-close:hover{color:var(--pdarker)}
.edit-lead-body{padding:16px 20px;overflow-y:auto;flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px}
.edit-field-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px}
.edit-field{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
.edit-field label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}
.edit-field input{padding:7px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:7px;font-size:12.5px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker);background:var(--p7);outline:none;transition:border-color .15s}
.edit-field input:focus{border-color:var(--p1);background:#fff}
.edit-lead-ft{padding:12px 20px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:flex-end;flex-shrink:0}
.edit-section-lbl{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:2px}

/* DASHBOARD DRAWER */
.dash-drawer-hd{padding:14px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0;background:#fff}
.dash-drawer-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker)}
.dash-drawer-close{font-size:22px;color:var(--gray2);cursor:pointer;line-height:1;transition:color .1s;padding:0 4px}
.dash-drawer-close:hover{color:var(--pdarker)}
.dash-drawer-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:11px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);transition:background .1s;cursor:pointer}
.dash-drawer-item:hover{background:var(--p7)}
.dash-drawer-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media(max-width:780px){.sidebar{width:180px}.dp{width:240px}.dash-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.dash-kpi-row{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}
@media(max-width:600px){.sidebar{display:none}.dp{width:200px}.dash-kpi-row{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}

/* ── MAIL ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.mail-wrap{display:flex;height:100%;overflow:hidden}
.mail-folders{width:176px;flex-shrink:0;border-right:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:var(--p7);padding:12px 8px;gap:2px;overflow-y:auto}
.mail-folder-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:8px;border:none;background:none;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--gray);cursor:pointer;text-align:left;width:100%;transition:background .12s}
.mail-folder-btn:hover{background:rgba(130,88,168,.07);color:var(--pdarker)}
.mail-folder-btn.active{background:rgba(130,88,168,.12);color:var(--p1);font-weight:700}
.mail-folder-btn .mail-f-count{margin-left:auto;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;background:var(--p1);color:#fff;padding:1px 6px;border-radius:8px;min-width:18px;text-align:center}
.mail-compose-btn{margin:4px 4px 10px;padding:9px 12px;background:var(--p1);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:9px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;justify-content:center;transition:opacity .15s}
.mail-compose-btn:hover{opacity:.88}
.mail-list{width:300px;flex-shrink:0;border-right:1px solid var(--border);overflow-y:auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.mail-list-hd{padding:12px 14px 8px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.mail-item{padding:11px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);cursor:pointer;transition:background .1s;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px}
.mail-item:hover{background:var(--p7)}
.mail-item.active{background:rgba(130,88,168,.07);border-left:3px solid var(--p1)}
.mail-item.unread .mail-from{font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker)}
.mail-item.unread .mail-subject{font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker)}
.mail-item-row1{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:6px}
.mail-from{font-size:12px;color:var(--gray);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;flex:1}
.mail-date{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray2);flex-shrink:0}
.mail-subject{font-size:12px;color:var(--pdarker);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
.mail-snippet{font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
.mail-unread-dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--p1);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.mail-reading{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.mail-reading-hd{padding:20px 24px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0}
.mail-reading-subject{font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:var(--pdarker);margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.3}
.mail-reading-meta{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;font-size:12px;color:var(--gray)}
.mail-reading-meta strong{color:var(--pdarker);font-weight:600}
.mail-reading-actions{padding:10px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;gap:8px;flex-shrink:0;background:var(--p7)}
.mail-reading-body{padding:24px;flex:1;font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#1e293b;overflow-y:auto}
.mail-reading-body pre{white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:inherit}
.mail-empty{flex:1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;color:var(--gray2)}
.mail-load-more{padding:10px;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0}
/* Compose modal */
.mail-compose-overlay{position:fixed;bottom:0;right:24px;width:520px;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:none;border-radius:12px 12px 0 0;box-shadow:0 -4px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.13);z-index:9999;display:flex;flex-direction:column;max-height:520px}
.mail-compose-hd{padding:12px 16px;background:var(--pdarker);color:#fff;border-radius:12px 12px 0 0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0}
.mail-compose-field{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.mail-compose-label{width:60px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray2);padding:8px 12px;flex-shrink:0}
.mail-compose-input{flex:1;border:none;outline:none;padding:8px 12px 8px 0;font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker)}
.mail-compose-body{flex:1;border:none;outline:none;padding:12px 16px;font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;line-height:1.6;resize:none;min-height:180px;color:var(--pdarker)}
.mail-compose-footer{padding:10px 14px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0}
/* ── CALENDAR ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.cal-wrap{display:flex;height:100%;overflow:hidden}
.cal-sidebar{width:220px;flex-shrink:0;border-right:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:var(--p7);padding:14px 10px;gap:2px;overflow-y:auto}
.cal-sidebar-hd{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.8px;padding:4px 8px 8px;margin-top:4px}
.cal-sidebar-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:8px;border:none;background:none;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--gray);cursor:pointer;text-align:left;width:100%;transition:background .12s}
.cal-sidebar-btn:hover{background:rgba(130,88,168,.07);color:var(--pdarker)}
.cal-sidebar-btn.active{background:rgba(130,88,168,.12);color:var(--p1);font-weight:700}
.cal-create-btn{margin:0 4px 12px;padding:9px 12px;background:var(--p1);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:9px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;justify-content:center;transition:opacity .15s}
.cal-create-btn:hover{opacity:.88}
.cal-color-dot{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
.cal-main{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden}
.cal-toolbar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:12px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0;background:#fff}
.cal-nav-btn{border:none;background:none;font-size:16px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--gray);padding:4px 8px;border-radius:6px;transition:background .12s;line-height:1}
.cal-nav-btn:hover{background:var(--p7);color:var(--pdarker)}
.cal-month-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:var(--pdarker);min-width:140px;text-align:center}
.cal-view-toggle{display:flex;gap:0;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;margin-left:auto}
.cal-view-btn{padding:5px 12px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;border:none;background:none;cursor:pointer;color:var(--gray);transition:background .12s}
.cal-view-btn.active{background:var(--p1);color:#fff}
.cal-sync-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:6px 12px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;background:#fff;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray);cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s}
.cal-sync-btn:hover{border-color:var(--p1);color:var(--p1)}
.cal-sync-btn.syncing{opacity:.6;pointer-events:none}
/* Month grid */
.cal-grid-wrap{flex:1;overflow:auto;padding:0}
.cal-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);border-left:1px solid var(--border);border-top:1px solid var(--border);min-width:0}
.cal-day-name{padding:8px 0;text-align:center;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.6px;color:var(--gray2);border-right:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:#fafafa}
.cal-cell{min-height:100px;padding:4px;border-right:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;cursor:pointer;transition:background .1s;position:relative}
.cal-cell:hover{background:var(--p7)}
.cal-cell.today{background:rgba(130,88,168,.04)}
.cal-cell.other-month{background:#fafafa}
.cal-cell.other-month .cal-day-num{opacity:.35}
.cal-day-num{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--pdarker);width:24px;height:24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;align-self:flex-start}
.cal-cell.today .cal-day-num{background:var(--p1);color:#fff;font-weight:800}
.cal-event-pill{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;cursor:pointer;line-height:1.4}
.cal-event-pill:hover{opacity:.85}
.cal-more-link{font-size:10px;color:var(--gray2);padding:1px 4px;cursor:pointer}
.cal-more-link:hover{color:var(--p1)}
/* Week view */
.cal-week-wrap{flex:1;display:flex;overflow:hidden}
.cal-week-time{width:52px;flex-shrink:0;border-right:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:40px}
.cal-week-hour-label{height:56px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:flex-end;padding-right:8px;padding-top:4px;font-size:10px;color:var(--gray2)}
.cal-week-cols{flex:1;display:grid;overflow:auto;position:relative}
.cal-week-day-hd{text-align:center;padding:8px 4px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);border-right:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;top:0;background:#fff;z-index:2}
.cal-week-day-hd.today{color:var(--p1)}
.cal-week-col{border-right:1px solid var(--border);position:relative;min-height:1344px}/* 24*56px */
.cal-week-cell{height:56px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray3);cursor:pointer}
.cal-week-cell:hover{background:var(--p7)}
.cal-week-event{position:absolute;left:2px;right:2px;border-radius:4px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;padding:2px 5px;overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;z-index:1}
/* Event modal */
.cal-modal-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.35);z-index:9000;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.cal-modal{background:#fff;border-radius:14px;width:480px;max-width:94vw;max-height:88vh;overflow-y:auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.18)}
.cal-modal-hd{padding:18px 20px 12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0}
.cal-modal-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:var(--pdarker);flex:1}
.cal-modal-body{padding:18px 20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px}
.cal-form-row{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
.cal-form-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.6px}
.cal-form-input{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:8px 12px;font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--pdarker);outline:none;transition:border-color .15s}
.cal-form-input:focus{border-color:var(--p1)}
.cal-form-row-2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px}
.cal-modal-footer{padding:12px 20px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:flex-end;gap:8px;flex-shrink:0}
/* Connect prompt */
.cal-connect-wrap{flex:1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;padding:40px}
/* Responsive */
@media(max-width:900px){.cal-sidebar{width:160px}}
@media(max-width:700px){.cal-sidebar{display:none}.cal-cell{min-height:64px}}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- LOGIN OVERLAY -->
<div class="login-overlay" id="login-overlay">
  <div class="login-card">
    <div class="login-logo">
      <img src="/login.png" alt="Vedio Sales" style="width:48px;height:48px;margin-bottom:6px">
      <div class="login-logo-title">Vedio Sales</div>
      <div class="login-logo-sub">Sales Pipeline Management</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Google sign-in (primary) -->
    <button class="login-google-btn" onclick="location.href='/api/auth/google'">
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><path fill="#4285F4" d="M17.64 9.2c0-.637-.057-1.251-.164-1.84H9v3.481h4.844c-.209 1.125-.843 2.078-1.796 2.717v2.258h2.908c1.702-1.567 2.684-3.874 2.684-6.615z"/><path fill="#34A853" d="M9 18c2.43 0 4.467-.806 5.956-2.18l-2.908-2.259c-.806.54-1.837.86-3.048.86-2.344 0-4.328-1.584-5.036-3.711H.957v2.332A8.997 8.997 0 0 0 9 18z"/><path fill="#FBBC05" d="M3.964 10.71A5.41 5.41 0 0 1 3.682 9c0-.593.102-1.17.282-1.71V4.958H.957A8.996 8.996 0 0 0 0 9c0 1.452.348 2.827.957 4.042l3.007-2.332z"/><path fill="#EA4335" d="M9 3.58c1.321 0 2.508.454 3.44 1.345l2.582-2.58C13.463.891 11.426 0 9 0A8.997 8.997 0 0 0 .957 4.958L3.964 6.29C4.672 4.163 6.656 3.58 9 3.58z"/></svg>
      Log ind med Google
    </button>

    <div class="login-err" id="login-err"></div>

    <!-- Email/password fallback -->
    <div class="login-divider"><div class="login-divider-line"></div><span class="login-divider-txt">eller</span><div class="login-divider-line"></div></div>
    <div class="login-fallback" id="login-fallback">
      <input class="login-inp" id="login-email" type="email" placeholder="Email" autocomplete="email">
      <input class="login-inp" id="login-pw" type="password" placeholder="Adgangskode" autocomplete="current-password"
        onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')doLogin()">
      <button class="login-btn" onclick="doLogin()">Log ind med email</button>
    </div>
    <button class="login-fallback-toggle" onclick="document.getElementById('login-fallback').classList.toggle('open');this.textContent=document.getElementById('login-fallback').classList.contains('open')?'Skjul email-login':'Log ind med email i stedet'">Log ind med email i stedet</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="app" id="app" style="display:none">

<!-- SIDEBAR -->
<aside class="sidebar" id="sb">
  <div class="sb-logo">
    <img id="logo-img" src="/login.png" alt="Vedio">
    <div>
      <div class="sb-logo-text">Vedio Sales</div>
      <div class="sb-logo-sub">Sales Pipeline Management</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <nav class="sb-nav">
    <a id="nv-dash" onclick="sv('dashboard')">
      <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><rect x="1" y="1" width="6" height="6" rx="1"/><rect x="9" y="1" width="6" height="6" rx="1"/><rect x="1" y="9" width="6" height="6" rx="1"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6" rx="1"/></svg>
      Dashboard
    </a>
    <a class="on" id="nv-s" onclick="sv('search')">
      <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><circle cx="7" cy="7" r="5"/><path d="m11 11 3 3"/></svg>
      Søg virksomheder
    </a>
    <a id="nv-l" onclick="sv('leads')">
      <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M2 4h12M2 8h8M2 12h6"/></svg>
      Mine leads
    </a>
    <a id="nv-deals" onclick="sv('deals')">
      <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><rect x="1" y="3" width="4" height="10" rx="1"/><rect x="6" y="6" width="4" height="7" rx="1"/><rect x="11" y="1" width="4" height="12" rx="1"/></svg>
      Deals
    </a>
    <a id="nv-calls" onclick="sv('calls')">
      <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M3 2a1 1 0 0 0-1 1c0 6.075 4.925 11 11 11a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-2.5a1 1 0 0 0-.553-.894L11 8.382a1 1 0 0 0-1.276.276L9 9.5C7.5 8.833 6.167 7.5 5.5 6l.842-.724A1 1 0 0 0 6.618 4L4.894 1.553A1 1 0 0 0 4 1H3a1 1 0 0 0-1 1Z" stroke-width="1.4"/></svg>
      Opkald
    </a>
    <a id="nv-mail" onclick="sv('mail')" style="position:relative">
      <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><rect x="1" y="3" width="14" height="10" rx="1.5"/><path d="M1 5l7 5 7-5"/></svg>
      Mail
      <span id="mail-badge" style="display:none;position:absolute;right:10px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);background:#ef4444;color:#fff;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:8px;min-width:16px;text-align:center"></span>
    </a>
    <a id="nv-calendar" onclick="sv('calendar')" style="position:relative">
      <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><rect x="1" y="2" width="14" height="13" rx="1.5"/><path d="M1 6h14M5 1v3M11 1v3"/></svg>
      Kalender
    </a>
    <a id="nv-tasks" onclick="sv('tasks')" style="position:relative">
      <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M2 4h12M2 8h12M2 12h7"/><circle cx="13" cy="12" r="2.5" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg>
      Opgaver
      <span id="task-badge" style="display:none;position:absolute;right:10px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);background:#ef4444;color:#fff;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:8px;min-width:16px;text-align:center"></span>
    </a>
  </nav>

  <div class="sb-filters" id="sb-filters" style="display:none"></div>

  <div class="sb-lists-wrap" id="sb-lists" style="display:none">
    <div class="sb-sec">Lister</div>
    <div id="lc"></div>
    <div class="sb-addlist" onclick="togNL()">＋ Ny liste</div>
    <input id="nli" class="nlinput" placeholder="Navn + Enter" style="display:none" autocomplete="off">
  </div>
  <div class="sb-footer" id="sb-footer" style="display:none">
    <button class="exp-btn" onclick="doExport()">⬇ Eksportér leads (CSV)</button>
  </div>

  <!-- USER PROFILE -->
  <div class="user-profile" id="user-profile" style="display:none">
    <div class="user-profile-inner" onclick="openProfileModal()" style="cursor:pointer" title="Rediger profil">
      <div class="user-avatar" id="user-avatar"></div>
      <div class="user-info">
        <div class="user-name" id="user-name"></div>
        <div class="user-role">
          <span class="role-badge" id="user-role-badge"></span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="user-logout" onclick="event.stopPropagation();sv('settings')" data-tip="Indstillinger"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="2.5"/><path d="M8 1v2M8 13v2M1 8h2M13 8h2M3.05 3.05l1.41 1.41M11.54 11.54l1.41 1.41M11.54 4.46l-1.41 1.41M4.46 11.54l-1.41 1.41"/></svg></div>
      <div class="user-logout" onclick="event.stopPropagation();logout()" data-tip="Log ud"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M6 2h7v12H6M2 8h8M8 5l3 3-3 3"/></svg></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>

<!-- MAIN -->
<main class="main">
  <div class="toolbar">
    <div class="sb-toggle" onclick="togSB()">☰</div>
    <div class="sbox" id="sw">
      <span class="sbox-ico">⌕</span>
      <input id="qs" type="text" placeholder="Hurtigsøg navn, CVR, branche, by…" autocomplete="off">
    </div>
    <div class="filter-btn" id="filter-btn-wrap">
      <button class="btn" onclick="togFilterPop()">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M1 3h14M3 8h10M5.5 13h5"/></svg>
        Filtre
        <span class="filter-count" id="filter-count" style="display:none">0</span>
      </button>
      <div class="fp-overlay" id="fp-overlay" onclick="togFilterPop()"></div>
      <div class="filter-popover" id="filter-popover">
        <div class="fp-hd">
          <span class="fp-title">Filtre</span>
          <button class="fp-close" onclick="togFilterPop()">✕</button>
        </div>
        <div class="fp-section">
          <div class="fp-section-title">Generelt</div>
          <div class="fl">Inkluder søgeord</div>
          <input class="fi" id="q" placeholder="CVR, navn, website…" autocomplete="off">
          <div class="fl">Ekskluder søgeord</div>
          <input class="fi" id="q-ex" placeholder="Holding, udlejning…" autocomplete="off">
          <div class="fl">Reklamebeskyttelse</div>
          <div class="rk-grp">
            <button class="rk-btn on" id="rk-alle" onclick="setRk('alle')">Alle</button>
            <button class="rk-btn" id="rk-skjul" onclick="setRk('skjul')">Skjul</button>
            <button class="rk-btn" id="rk-kun" onclick="setRk('kun')">Kun</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fp-section">
          <div class="fp-section-title">Virksomhedsoplysninger</div>
          <div class="fl">Virksomhedsform</div>
          <select class="fs" id="f-form" onchange="applyF()">
            <option value="">Alle former</option>
            <option value="ApS">ApS</option><option value="A/S">A/S</option>
            <option value="I/S">I/S</option><option value="Enkeltmands">Enkeltmands</option>
          </select>
          <div class="fl">Ansatte</div>
          <div class="frow"><input class="fi" id="fe1" type="number" placeholder="Fra" onchange="applyF()"><span>–</span><input class="fi" id="fe2" type="number" placeholder="Til" onchange="applyF()"></div>
          <div class="fl">Egenkapital over (kr.)</div>
          <input class="fi" id="f-eq" type="number" placeholder="0" onchange="applyF()">
          <div class="fl">Resultat over (kr.)</div>
          <input class="fi" id="f-res" type="number" placeholder="0" onchange="applyF()">
          <div class="fl">Virksomhedens alder (mdr.)</div>
          <div class="frow"><input class="fi" id="fam" type="number" placeholder="Min" onchange="applyF()"><span>–</span><input class="fi" id="faM" type="number" placeholder="Max" onchange="applyF()"></div>
          <div class="fl">Branche</div>
          <select class="fs" id="f-b" onchange="applyF()">
            <option value="">Alle brancher</option>
            <option value="41">Byggeri & anlæg</option>
            <option value="43">Spec. byggeri</option>
            <option value="46">Engroshandel</option>
            <option value="47">Detailhandel</option>
            <option value="56">Restaurant & café</option>
            <option value="62">IT & software</option>
            <option value="63">Data & hosting</option>
            <option value="64">Finansiering</option>
            <option value="68">Ejendomme</option>
            <option value="69">Jura & revision</option>
            <option value="70">Rådgivning</option>
            <option value="71">Arkitekter</option>
            <option value="73">Reklame & marketing</option>
            <option value="81">Rengøring</option>
            <option value="86">Sundhed</option>
          </select>
          <div class="fl">Stiftet (år)</div>
          <div class="frow"><input class="fi" id="fy1" type="number" placeholder="2000" onchange="applyF()"><span>–</span><input class="fi" id="fy2" type="number" placeholder="2025" onchange="applyF()"></div>
          <div class="fl">ICP-score minimum</div>
          <select class="fs" id="f-icp" onchange="applyF()">
            <option value="0">Alle</option><option value="3">3+ ★</option><option value="4">4+ ★</option><option value="5">5 ★ kun</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="fp-section">
          <div class="fp-section-title">Pipeline-fase</div>
          <div class="chip-grp">
            <div class="chip" onclick="tChipStage(this,'Ny')">Ny</div>
            <div class="chip" onclick="tChipStage(this,'Kvalificeret')">Kvalificeret</div>
            <div class="chip" onclick="tChipStage(this,'I dialog')">I dialog</div>
            <div class="chip" onclick="tChipStage(this,'Tilbud')">Tilbud</div>
            <div class="chip" onclick="tChipStage(this,'Vundet')">Vundet</div>
            <div class="chip" onclick="tChipStage(this,'Tabt')">Tabt</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fp-section">
          <div class="fp-section-title">Område</div>
          <div class="fl">Inkluder by</div>
          <input class="fi" id="f-ci" placeholder="Aalborg" autocomplete="off" onchange="applyF()">
          <div class="fl">Ekskluder by</div>
          <input class="fi" id="f-cx" placeholder="København" autocomplete="off" onchange="applyF()">
          <div class="fl">Postnr. interval</div>
          <div class="frow"><input class="fi" id="fzm" type="number" placeholder="5000" onchange="applyF()"><span>–</span><input class="fi" id="fzM" type="number" placeholder="5999" onchange="applyF()"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="fp-footer">
          <button class="btn btn-sm" style="width:100%;justify-content:center" onclick="resetF()">Nulstil alle filtre</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-left:auto;display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="addAll()">+ Tilføj alle</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="stbar" id="stbar"></div>
  <div class="selbar h" id="selbar"></div>

  <!-- LEADS LIST BAR (moved from sidebar) -->
  <div class="leads-list-bar" id="leads-list-bar" style="display:none">
    <div class="llb-lists" id="llb-lists"></div>
    <div class="llb-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="togNL('nli2','inline-block')">+ Ny liste</button>
      <input id="nli2" class="llb-input" placeholder="Navn + Enter" style="display:none" autocomplete="off">
      <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="doExport()">⬇ Eksportér leads (CSV)</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="body-wrap">
    <div class="tw">
      <table id="tbl"><thead id="thead"></thead><tbody id="tbody"></tbody></table>
      <div id="load-more-wrap" style="display:none;padding:12px;text-align:center">
        <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="loadMore()" id="load-more-btn">Indlæs flere resultater</button>
        <span id="load-more-info" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);margin-left:8px"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SETTINGS PANEL -->
  <div id="settings-panel" style="display:none;flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:24px 32px;background:var(--white)">
    <h2 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker);margin-bottom:20px">Indstillinger</h2>

    <!-- Integrationer -->
    <div style="background:var(--p7);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:16px">
      <h3 style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px">
        <span style="background:#ea4b71;color:#fff;width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:4px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">n</span>
        n8n Webhook <span class="int-status int-no" id="n8n-status-s">Ikke konfigureret</span>
      </h3>
      <p style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--gray);margin-bottom:10px">Push leads direkte til dine n8n workflows som JSON payload.</p>
      <input id="n8n-url-s" placeholder="https://your-n8n.cloud/webhook/…" style="width:100%;max-width:480px;margin-bottom:8px;padding:6px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;outline:none">
      <div style="display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap">
        <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="saveN8nS()">Gem webhook</button>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="pushToN8n()">Send alle leads →</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Twilio Dialer -->
    <div style="background:var(--p7);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:16px">
      <h3 style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">
        <span style="background:#f22f46;color:#fff;width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:4px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0">T</span>
        Twilio Dialer <span class="int-status int-no" id="twilio-status-badge">Tjekker…</span>
      </h3>
      <p style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--gray);margin-bottom:12px;line-height:1.6">
        Ring direkte fra platformen via Twilio Voice. Browser-baseret opkald — ingen separat app. Kræver konfiguration af miljøvariabler på serveren.
      </p>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:12px 14px;margin-bottom:12px;font-size:12px;line-height:1.9;color:var(--pdarker)">
        <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:6px">Opsætning — tilføj til din .env fil</div>
        <code style="display:block;background:var(--p7);border-radius:6px;padding:10px 12px;font-size:11px;color:#0f172a;line-height:2;font-family:monospace">TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=ACxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx<br>TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_auth_token<br>TWILIO_FROM_NUMBER=+4512345678<br>TWILIO_TWIML_APP_SID=APxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx</code>
        <div style="margin-top:8px;font-size:11px;color:var(--gray)">
          1. Opret en gratis Twilio-konto på <a href="https://twilio.com" target="_blank" style="color:var(--p1)">twilio.com</a><br>
          2. Tilføj et dansk nummer (+45) under Phone Numbers<br>
          3. Opret en TwiML App under Voice → TwiML Apps og sæt Request URL til <code style="background:var(--p7);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px">https://din-server.dk/api/twilio/voice</code><br>
          4. Genstart serveren — status skifter til grøn herover
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
        <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="checkTwilioStatus()">Tjek forbindelse</button>
        <span id="twilio-cap-label" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gray)"></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Gmail Integration -->
    <div style="background:var(--p7);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:16px">
      <h3 style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">
        <span style="background:#ea4335;color:#fff;width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:4px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0">G</span>
        Gmail <span class="int-status int-no" id="gmail-status-badge">Tjekker…</span>
      </h3>
      <p style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--gray);margin-bottom:12px;line-height:1.6">Læs og send mails direkte fra platformen via din Gmail-konto.</p>

      <!-- Step 1: OAuth credentials setup (hidden once configured) -->
      <div id="gmail-setup-section">
        <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:12px 14px;margin-bottom:12px">
          <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:8px">
            Trin 1 — Opret Google OAuth App
          </div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:10px">
            1. Gå til <a href="https://console.cloud.google.com" target="_blank" style="color:var(--p1);font-weight:600">console.cloud.google.com</a> → Opret projekt<br>
            2. Aktivér <strong>Gmail API</strong> under APIs &amp; Services → Bibliotek<br>
            3. OAuth-samtykkeskærm → Ekstern → tilføj din email som testbruger<br>
            4. Legitimationsoplysninger → Opret OAuth-klient-id → Webapplikation<br>
            5. Tilføj denne <strong>Redirect URI</strong>: <code id="gmail-redirect-uri-display" style="background:var(--p7);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;font-size:10.5px;cursor:pointer" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.textContent).then(()=>showToast('Kopieret!'))">http://localhost:3000/api/mail/callback</code>
          </div>
          <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:8px">
            Trin 2 — Indsæt dine nøgler
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;max-width:480px">
            <input id="gmail-client-id-input" placeholder="Client ID  (…apps.googleusercontent.com)" style="padding:7px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;outline:none;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box">
            <input id="gmail-client-secret-input" type="password" placeholder="Client Secret" style="padding:7px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;outline:none;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box">
            <button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" onclick="saveGmailConfig()" style="align-self:flex-start;padding:7px 18px">Gem og fortsæt →</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2: Connect account (shown once credentials are saved) -->
      <div id="gmail-connect-section" style="display:none">
        <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
          <button class="btn btn-primary" id="gmail-connect-btn" onclick="connectGmail()" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 18px;font-size:13px">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><path d="M17.64 9.2c0-.637-.057-1.251-.164-1.84H9v3.481h4.844c-.209 1.125-.843 2.078-1.796 2.717v2.258h2.908c1.702-1.567 2.684-3.874 2.684-6.615z" fill="#4285F4"/><path d="M9 18c2.43 0 4.467-.806 5.956-2.184l-2.908-2.258c-.806.54-1.837.86-3.048.86-2.344 0-4.328-1.584-5.036-3.711H.957v2.332C2.438 15.983 5.482 18 9 18z" fill="#34A853"/><path d="M3.964 10.707c-.18-.54-.282-1.117-.282-1.707s.102-1.167.282-1.707V4.961H.957C.347 6.175 0 7.55 0 9s.348 2.826.957 4.039l3.007-2.332z" fill="#FBBC05"/><path d="M9 3.58c1.321 0 2.508.454 3.44 1.345l2.582-2.58C13.463.891 11.426 0 9 0 5.482 0 2.438 2.017.957 4.961L3.964 7.293C4.672 5.166 6.656 3.58 9 3.58z" fill="#EA4335"/></svg>
            Forbind med Google
          </button>
          <button class="btn btn-sm" id="gmail-disconnect-btn" onclick="disconnectGmail()" style="display:none;background:#fef2f2;color:#dc2626;border-color:#fecaca">Afbryd forbindelse</button>
          <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="resetGmailConfig()" style="color:var(--gray);font-size:11px">Skift nøgler</button>
          <span id="gmail-cap-label" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gray)"></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Social Media / Enrichment - moved to inline below -->
    <div style="background:var(--p7);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:16px">
      <h3 style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px">Social Media &amp; Enrichment</h3>
      <div style="background:#fef9c3;border:1px solid #fde047;border-radius:6px;padding:8px 10px;font-size:11.5px;color:#713f12;margin-bottom:12px">
        Direkte scraping af Instagram, TikTok og Facebook er imod deres servicevilkår og kan medføre blokering. Her er lovlige alternativer.
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:12px">
        <strong style="color:var(--pdarker)">Manuel tilføjelse:</strong> Tilføj sociale links direkte på hvert lead-kort.<br>
        <strong style="color:var(--pdarker)">Phantombuster:</strong> Lovlig automation til offentlige profil-URLs via dine login-sessioner.<br>
        <strong style="color:var(--pdarker)">Clearbit / Apollo.io / Hunter.io:</strong> Betalte enrichment-APIs der leverer sociale links og email baseret på CVR/domæne.
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:6px">API-nøgler</div>
      <input id="clearbit-key-s" placeholder="Clearbit API nøgle (sk_…)" style="width:100%;max-width:480px;margin-bottom:6px;padding:6px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;outline:none;display:block">
      <input id="apollo-key-s" placeholder="Apollo.io API nøgle" style="width:100%;max-width:480px;margin-bottom:6px;padding:6px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;outline:none;display:block">
      <input id="phantombuster-key-s" placeholder="Phantombuster API nøgle" style="width:100%;max-width:480px;margin-bottom:8px;padding:6px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;outline:none;display:block">
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="saveEnrichKeysS()">Gem nøgler</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- DEALS PANEL -->
  <div id="deals-panel" style="display:none;flex:1;overflow:hidden;flex-direction:column;background:var(--p7)">
    <div class="deals-hd">
      <div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker)">Deals</div>
      <div id="deals-summary" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gray)"></div>
    </div>
    <div id="deals-board" class="kb-board"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- TASKS PANEL -->
  <div id="tasks-panel" style="display:none;flex:1;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden;background:var(--white)">
    <div class="deals-hd">
      <div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--pdarker)">Opgaver</div>
      <div id="tasks-summary" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gray)"></div>
    </div>
    <div id="tasks-body" class="tasks-page"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- DASHBOARD PANEL -->
  <div id="dashboard-panel" style="display:none;flex:1;overflow-y:auto;background:var(--p7)">
    <!-- rendered by rDashboard() -->
  </div>

  <!-- CALLS PANEL -->
  <div id="calls-panel" style="display:none;flex:1;overflow:hidden;flex-direction:column;background:var(--p7)">
    <!-- rendered by rCalls() -->
  </div>

  <!-- MAIL PANEL -->
  <div id="mail-panel" style="display:none;flex:1;overflow:hidden;flex-direction:column;background:#fff">
    <!-- rendered by rMail() -->
  </div>

  <!-- CALENDAR PANEL -->
  <div id="calendar-panel" style="display:none;flex:1;overflow:hidden;flex-direction:column;background:#fff">
    <!-- rendered by rCalendar() -->
  </div>
</main>
</div>

<!-- DETAIL PANEL (fixed, root-level so it works from any view) -->
<div class="dp h" id="dp" style="position:fixed;right:0;top:0;bottom:0;z-index:200;background:#fff;box-shadow:-6px 0 32px rgba(0,0,0,.18);border-left:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-direction:column"></div>

<!-- DEAL CARD BACKDROP -->
<div id="dp-bd" style="display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.4);z-index:199" onclick="hdDp()"></div>

<!-- PROFILE MODAL -->
<div id="profile-modal" style="display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:320;background:rgba(0,0,0,.45);align-items:center;justify-content:center">
  <div class="profile-modal-card">
    <div class="profile-modal-hd">
      <span class="profile-modal-title">Min profil</span>
      <span class="profile-modal-close" onclick="closeProfileModal()">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-modal-body">

      <!-- Avatar -->
      <div class="profile-avatar-wrap">
        <div class="profile-avatar-ring" onclick="document.getElementById('profile-avatar-input').click()" title="Skift profilbillede">
          <div class="profile-avatar-big" id="profile-avatar-big"></div>
          <div class="profile-avatar-cam"><div class="profile-avatar-cam-ico"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:10.5px;color:var(--gray2)">Klik for at uploade billede</div>
        <input id="profile-avatar-input" type="file" accept="image/*" style="display:none" onchange="handleAvatarUpload(this)">
        <button id="profile-avatar-remove" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" style="display:none;font-size:11px;padding:4px 10px" onclick="removeAvatar()">Fjern billede</button>
      </div>

      <div class="profile-msg" id="profile-msg"></div>

      <!-- Name + Email -->
      <div class="profile-field">
        <label>Navn</label>
        <input id="pf-name" type="text" placeholder="Dit fulde navn">
      </div>
      <div class="profile-field">
        <label>Email</label>
        <input id="pf-email" type="email" placeholder="din@email.dk">
      </div>

      <!-- Color -->
      <div class="profile-field">
        <label>Profilfarve</label>
        <div class="profile-color-row" id="profile-color-row">
          <!-- swatches rendered by JS -->
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="profile-divider">

      <!-- Password change -->
      <div class="profile-pw-toggle" onclick="togglePwSection()">
        <span id="pw-toggle-arrow">▶</span> Skift adgangskode
      </div>
      <div class="profile-pw-section" id="profile-pw-section" style="display:none">
        <div class="profile-field">
          <label>Nuværende adgangskode</label>
          <input id="pf-pw-current" type="password" placeholder="••••••••" autocomplete="current-password">
        </div>
        <div class="profile-field">
          <label>Ny adgangskode</label>
          <input id="pf-pw-new" type="password" placeholder="••••••••" autocomplete="new-password">
        </div>
        <div class="profile-field">
          <label>Bekræft ny adgangskode</label>
          <input id="pf-pw-confirm" type="password" placeholder="••••••••" autocomplete="new-password">
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-sm" style="width:100%;justify-content:center" onclick="changePassword()">Skift adgangskode</button>
      </div>

    </div>
    <div class="profile-modal-ft">
      <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="closeProfileModal()">Annuller</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="saveProfile()">Gem profil</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- EDIT LEAD MODAL -->
<div id="edit-lead-modal" style="display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:310;background:rgba(0,0,0,.45);align-items:center;justify-content:center">
  <div class="edit-lead-card">
    <div class="edit-lead-hd">
      <span class="edit-lead-title" id="edit-lead-title">Rediger lead</span>
      <span class="edit-lead-close" onclick="closeEditLead()">×</span>
    </div>
    <div class="edit-lead-body">
      <div class="edit-section-lbl">Kontaktperson</div>
      <div class="edit-field-row">
        <div class="edit-field">
          <label>Kontaktnavn</label>
          <input id="ef-contactName" placeholder="Fuldt navn">
        </div>
        <div class="edit-field">
          <label>Titel / stilling</label>
          <input id="ef-contactTitle" placeholder="CEO, Marketing Manager…">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="edit-field-row">
        <div class="edit-field">
          <label>Telefon</label>
          <input id="ef-ph" placeholder="12 34 56 78">
        </div>
        <div class="edit-field">
          <label>Email</label>
          <input id="ef-em" type="email" placeholder="kontakt@firma.dk">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="edit-field">
        <label>Website</label>
        <input id="ef-web" placeholder="www.firma.dk">
      </div>
      <div class="edit-section-lbl" style="margin-top:4px">Virksomhed</div>
      <div class="edit-field">
        <label>Firmanavn</label>
        <input id="ef-name" placeholder="Firmanavn">
      </div>
      <div class="edit-field">
        <label>Branche</label>
        <input id="ef-ind" placeholder="Detailhandel, Teknologi…">
      </div>
      <div class="edit-field">
        <label>Adresse</label>
        <input id="ef-addr" placeholder="Vejnavn 1">
      </div>
      <div class="edit-field-row">
        <div class="edit-field">
          <label>Postnr.</label>
          <input id="ef-zip" placeholder="1234">
        </div>
        <div class="edit-field">
          <label>By</label>
          <input id="ef-city" placeholder="København">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="edit-field-row">
        <div class="edit-field">
          <label>Omsætning (kr.)</label>
          <input id="ef-omsaetning" type="number" placeholder="0">
        </div>
        <div class="edit-field">
          <label>Ansatte</label>
          <input id="ef-emps" type="number" placeholder="0">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="edit-lead-ft">
      <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="closeEditLead()">Annuller</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="saveEditLead()">Gem ændringer</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- DASHBOARD DETAIL DRAWER -->
<div id="dash-drawer" style="display:none;position:fixed;right:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:360px;z-index:251;background:#fff;box-shadow:-6px 0 32px rgba(0,0,0,.16);border-left:1px solid var(--border);flex-direction:column">
  <div class="dash-drawer-hd">
    <span class="dash-drawer-title" id="dash-drawer-title"></span>
    <span class="dash-drawer-close" onclick="closeDashDrawer()">×</span>
  </div>
  <div id="dash-drawer-body" style="flex:1;overflow-y:auto"></div>
</div>
<div id="dash-drawer-bd" style="display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.28);z-index:250" onclick="closeDashDrawer()"></div>

<!-- INTEGRATIONS MODAL -->
<div class="modal-bg h" id="int-modal">
  <div class="modal">
    <h3>n8n Integration</h3>
    <p>Push leads direkte til dine n8n workflows som JSON payload.</p>
    <div class="modal-section">
      <h4>
        <span style="background:#ea4b71;color:#fff;width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:4px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">n</span>
        n8n Webhook <span class="int-status int-no" id="n8n-status">Ikke konfigureret</span>
      </h4>
      <input id="n8n-url" placeholder="https://your-n8n.cloud/webhook/…">
      <div style="display:flex;gap:5px">
        <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="saveN8n()">Gem webhook</button>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="pushToN8n()">Send alle leads →</button>
      </div>
      <p style="margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:0;font-size:10.5px;color:#6b7280;line-height:1.5">Sender et JSON payload med alle felter: CVR, kontaktoplysninger, sociale profiler, ICP-score, pipeline-fase, noter og tags. Trigger dine n8n workflows til CRM, email, Slack m.m.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-section">
      <h4>CSV / Manuel eksport</h4>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap">
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="doExport()">⬇ Alle leads</button>
        <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="expSel()">⬇ Valgte leads</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-section" style="background:var(--p7);border-radius:8px;padding:10px;border:1px solid var(--border)">
      <h4 style="margin-bottom:6px;font-size:11.5px">n8n workflow-idéer</h4>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.6">
        • Push til HubSpot, Pipedrive eller Salesforce<br>
        • Send Slack-besked til SDR ved nyt lead<br>
        • Opret automatisk follow-up-task i Notion/Asana<br>
        • Berig med Apollo/Clearbit og skriv tilbage til Vedio Leads<br>
        • Send personlig cold email via Instantly/Lemlist
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="closeInt()">Luk</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SOCIAL MEDIA GUIDE MODAL -->
<div class="modal-bg h" id="social-modal">
  <div class="modal">
    <h3>Social Media Integration</h3>
    <div class="social-note">Direkte scraping af Instagram, TikTok og Facebook er imod deres servicevilkår og kan medføre blokering. Her er lovlige alternativer:</div>
    <div class="modal-section">
      <h4>Hvad vi kan gøre</h4>
      <p style="font-size:11.5px;color:#374151;margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.5"><strong>Manuel tilføjelse:</strong> SDR tilføjer sociale links direkte på hvert lead-kort. Bruges til opfølgning via DM.</p>
      <p style="font-size:11.5px;color:#374151;margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.5"><strong>Phantombuster:</strong> Lovlig automation der udtrækker offentlige profil-URLs fra LinkedIn, Instagram m.fl. via din egne login-sessioner.</p>
      <p style="font-size:11.5px;color:#374151;margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.5"><strong>Clearbit / Apollo.io / Hunter.io:</strong> Betalte enrichment-APIs der leverer sociale links, email og LinkedIn-URL baseret på CVR/domæne.</p>
      <p style="font-size:11.5px;color:#374151;line-height:1.5"><strong>Facebook Graph API:</strong> Gratis for virksomheders egne sider. Kræver business-konto og brugeraccept.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-section">
      <h4>Konfigurér enrichment-API</h4>
      <input id="clearbit-key" placeholder="Clearbit API nøgle (sk_…)">
      <input id="apollo-key" placeholder="Apollo.io API nøgle">
      <input id="phantombuster-key" placeholder="Phantombuster API nøgle">
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="saveEnrichKeys()">Gem nøgler</button>
      <p style="margin-top:6px;margin-bottom:0;font-size:10.5px;color:#6b7280">I server-versionen bruges disse nøgler til at berige leads automatisk ved tilføjelse.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-section">
      <h4>Tilgængelige social media felter per lead</h4>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px">
        <span class="pill pill-p1">Instagram URL</span>
        <span class="pill pill-p1">Facebook side</span>
        <span class="pill pill-p1">TikTok profil</span>
        <span class="pill pill-p1">LinkedIn virksomhed</span>
        <span class="pill pill-p1">Website</span>
        <span class="pill pill-p1">Follower-estimat</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="closeSocialGuide()">Luk</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

